nes egne aldersgrenser for enkelt yrkesgrupper som piloter, leger og politi.", "Selv om Hack mener aldersgrensen b\u00f8r oppheves, roser hun Norge for \u00e5 ha satt en relativt h\u00f8y alminnelig aldersgrense p\u00e5 72 \u00e5r."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|helse"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "50e8f8a018fbe13c1ae35c383858d64ea75a9f97296c34313fffb69063a19c5b"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-01-10T21:20:23.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "I dag innf\u00f8res den nye arbeidsmilj\u00f8loven hvor ansatte kan jobbe til de er 72 \u00e5r. Jussjurist mener mange burde f\u00e5 jobbe lenger."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11266627.ece/gui2l7/ALTERNATES/w980-default/eldre%20i%20jobb.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/5fb7f12d23ee562c58b01adcfbd8517888a95293.jpg?593fe4f9"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["\u2013 Trenger ikke en \u00f8vre aldersgrense i arbeidslivet -adressa.no", "M\u00e5 se p\u00e5 annet enn juss", "Hevet aldersgrensen"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "5fb7f12d23ee562c58b01adcfbd8517888a95293"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "helse"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "careers"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["\u00f8vre aldersgrense", "arbeidsliv", "aldersgrense", "aldring"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "norge"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "melanie regine hack"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/helse"]}, {"field": "og-image", "